title: Stop Looking!  We Have Your New Home!
posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OHR/NJRH', 'Pennbrooke offers apartment and townhome living, located on the banks of Nine Mile Creek in Bloomington.', 'Enjoy our indoor pool and sauna, party room with full kitchen, fitness center, and BBQ area with a private courtyard.', 'Choose from a studio, one- or two- bedroom apartment, or a one- or two- bedroom townhomes.', 'We have professional on-site management and maintenance.', 'Telecommuting?', 'Pennbrooke has fiber-optic internet service available!', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Pennbrooke home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Balcony or patio options', 'Window coverings', 'Additional storage', 'Walk-in closet', 'Fireplace - in select homes', 'Ceiling fan', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Community Amenities', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Elevator access', 'Trash chutes', 'Laundry facility', 'Fitness center', 'Indoor swimming pool', 'Sauna', 'Party room', 'Library', 'Media center', 'Off street parking', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Car wash station', 'Pennbrooke Apartments Information', 'Address:', '2400 W 102nd St, Minneapolis MN, 55431', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=18', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Fee:', '$100 - 200 (Note: varies by pet, non-refundable)', 'Pet Deposit:', '$200 (Note: per pet)', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Saturday:', '10:00AM - 4:00PM', 'Sunday:', '12:00PM - 4:00PM']
